This is the exercise proposed in the Ruby on Rails session for the Igalia and URJC's Master of Software Libre (http://www.mastersoftwarelibre.com/)

The code corresponds to demo application proposed in the "Rails Guided Exercise: Creating a Blog" and the solution for the first of the three proposed exercises (2.1. Add authors)

The description of the exercise is in the html doc "Rails_guided_exercise_Creating_a_blog.html". (The code is made from scratch, it is not got from the GIT repository proposed at the beginning of the exercise.)

